### Cycle 1 — Scaffolding (AI Stub + Auth + CRUD) — Status: ❌ Belum

#### [NEW] Model files di `src/models/`
Perlu dibuat file DB query layer (menggunakan `pg` pool) untuk tabel:
- `users.js` — `createUser`, `findByEmail`, `findById`
- [goals.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/routes/goals.js) — `createGoal`, `listByUser`, `updateGoal`, `deleteGoal`
- [tasks.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/routes/tasks.js) — `insertTasks`, `listByGoal`, `updateStatus`
- `ai_recommendations.js` — `savePendingRecommendation`, `updateStatus`

#### [MODIFY] [middleware/authenticate.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/middleware/authenticate.js)
- Implementasi JWT `Bearer` token verification menggunakan `jsonwebtoken`
- Set `req.user = { id, email }` jika valid

#### [MODIFY] [routes/auth.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/routes/auth.js)
- `POST /register` — hash password dengan `bcryptjs`, simpan ke tabel `users` + buat `profile`
- `POST /login` — verifikasi password, return JWT access token
- `GET /me` — return user info dari `req.user`

#### [MODIFY] [routes/goals.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/routes/goals.js)
- `POST /` — buat goal baru
- `GET /` — list semua goal user
- `PATCH /:id` — update goal
- `DELETE /:id` — hapus goal
- Semua route dilindungi [authenticate](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/middleware/authenticate.js#1-6) middleware

#### [MODIFY] [routes/ai.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/routes/ai.js)
- `POST /plan/suggest` — endpoint yang memanggil [callLLM](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/services/llm.js#19-23), menyimpan `ai_recommendations`, dan return saran

#### [MODIFY] [services/llm.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/services/llm.js)
- Implementasi [callLLM(prompt, context)](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/services/llm.js#19-23):
  1. Baca [system.md](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/prompts/system.md) sebagai system prompt
  2. Bangun user prompt dari `context` (goal, profil, task sudah ada)
  3. Hubungkan ke Gemini via `@google/generative-ai` menggunakan `config.geminiKey`
  4. Tambahkan **mock mode**: jika `LLM_PROVIDER=mock` (env), return fixture JSON tanpa memanggil API
  5. Panggil [validateAIOutput](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/services/llm.js#23-31) pada hasil, log hasilnya dengan `logger`

#### [MODIFY] [routes/tasks.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/routes/tasks.js)
- `POST /` — simpan satu/banyak task (hasil accept dari AI) ke tabel `tasks`
- `GET /` — list tasks berdasarkan `goal_id`
- `PATCH /:id/status` — update status task (`todo → done`)

#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/app.js)
- Uncomment dan daftarkan `authRoutes`, `goalRoutes`, `aiRoutes`, `taskRoutes`

