## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests (yang sudah ada)
```bash
cd server
npm test
```
Smoke test ([smoke.test.js](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/tests/smoke.test.js)) sudah ada dan akan memverifikasi `GET /health` dan `GET /metrics`.

### Tests Baru yang Perlu Ditambahkan
Setelah implementasi selesai, perlu ditambahkan:

1. **Unit test untuk [validateAIOutput](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/services/llm.js#23-31)** — test input JSON valid, invalid, dan malformed
2. **Unit test untuk [callLLM](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/src/services/llm.js#19-23) (mock mode)** — test bahwa mock mengembalikan output sesuai `SuggestionSchema`
3. **Integration test untuk `POST /api/auth/register` dan `POST /api/auth/login`**
4. **Integration test untuk `POST /api/ai/plan/suggest`** menggunakan mock LLM provider

### Manual Verification
Setelah server berjalan (`npm run dev`), lakukan:

1. **Test health check:**
   ```
   GET http://localhost:3000/health
   → Expect: { "status": "ok" }
   ```

2. **Test register + login:**
   ```
   POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
   Body: { "email": "test@test.com", "password": "password123" }
   → Expect: 201 Created + { token: "..." }
   ```

3. **Test AI suggest (mock mode):**
   - Set `LLM_PROVIDER=mock` di [.env](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/Dicoding%202/capstoneprojek/capstone-case-ai-web-dev-starter/server/.env)
   ```
   POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/plan/suggest
   Header: Authorization: Bearer <token>
   Body: { "goal_id": "<uuid>" }
   → Expect: 200 + array tasks sesuai SuggestionSchema
   ```

4. Periksa log di terminal — setiap request harus muncul log JSON dari Pino.
